title: *PATREON PREVIEW* Chuck Crunched The Numbers, It’s Disgusting
description:
It’s vintage TF this week, both literally and figuratively, as the Core 4 lock in with our best friends behind the paywall for our 4th podcast in 3 days, but you wouldn’t know that from our pure, unbridled enthusiasm for each other’s company! From Jimmy and Larry’s man date digging in the crates and general thoughts on copping secondhand, to the embarrassing reality of trying to explain what you do for a living as a professional podcaster and one last check-in with Chuck ahead of this weekend’s 24 in 24 glizzy challenge livestream, The Only Podcast That Matters™ always delivers.
 
For more Throwing Fits, check us out on Patreon: www.patreon.com/throwingfits.
